 border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Allegri t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 sau 60 ph\u00fat. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tim \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n run d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. H\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Massimiliano Allegri noi ve tran Real Madrid vs Juventus hinh anh\" title=\"Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-juventus-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-184056.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Juventus </strong></span>gi\u00fap Los Blancos \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMassimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 2 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, nh\u01b0ng Juventus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 ch\u1ec9 sau 60 ph\u00fat. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"T\u1ed1i nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus than v\u00e3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb: \u201cJuventus \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1edd t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Massimiliano Allegri noi ve tran Real Madrid vs Juventus hinh anh 2\" title=\"Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Massimiliano-Allegri-noi-ve-tran-Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Buffon c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMario Mandzukic th\u00ec chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, song t\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u01a1i bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSami Khedira c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i: \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc khi Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1069","checkdouble":"184073"},{"date":"07:04 12/04","title":"\u0110\u01b0a Real v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/12/dua-real-vao-ban-ket-champions-league-cristiano-ronaldo-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolu