\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo noi ve tran Real Madrid vs Juventus hinh anh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/dua-real-vao-ban-ket-champions-league-cristiano-ronaldo-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a CR7 gi\u00fap Real Madrid v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus 4-3 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-kich-ban-tai-bernabeu-nam-ngoai-suc-tuong-tuong-cua-toi-184-184065.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn</strong></span>, \u00f4ng r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u00e2u s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, b\u1edfi v\u1eady khi b\u1ea1n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m th\u00ec t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mang v\u1ec1 cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ng\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam sau tr\u1eadn Real vs Juventus: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ea3. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o y\u1ebfu c\u1ea3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban thang cua Ronaldo dua Real vao ban ket Champions League\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0a Real v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Thong-ke-Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-1-3-Nhung-con-so-kinh-ngac-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Ronaldo c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi th\u00eam th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng: \u201cT\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ghi th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Real \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1068","checkdouble":"184074"},{"date":"06:21 12/04","title":"V\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, HLV Bayern n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/vao-ban-ket-champions-league-hlv-bayern-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f