r\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Montella phat bieu ve tran Bayern Munich vs Sevilla\" title=\"Montella ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/thay-tro-montella-nghen-ngao-noi-loi-chia-tay-champions-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vincenzo Montella ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/vao-ban-ket-champions-league-hlv-bayern-noi-gi-184-184067.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Jupp Heynckes \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Sevilla</strong></span>, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. Sau \u0111\u00f3 Vincenzo Montella ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Sevilla, \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi Sevilla kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn nghe th\u1ea5y NHM ca h\u00e1t sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV c\u1ee7a Sevilla&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sevilla tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-bayern-munich-vs-sevilla-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-184055.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Bayern Munich vs Sevilla</strong></span> khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd Jose Castro v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chu tich Sevilla, Jose Castro len tieng sau khi khong the vao ban ket\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sevilla, Jose Castro l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/sevilla.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sevilla, Jose Castro l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Bayern Munich, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Sevilla \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Sevilla, Sergio Escudero cho r\u1eb1ng: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1066","checkdouble":"184068"},{"date":"05:41 12/04","title":"Buffon v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/buffon-va-ky-niem-buon-trong-tran-cuoi-cung-tai-champions-league.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-fa