>V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh (d\u00f9 ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n), c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus 1-3 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, Juve \u0111ang ch\u1edd ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, th\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trung v\u1ec7 Benatia ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Vazquez, qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Qu\u00e1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver, Buffon \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon nhan the do trong tran dau cuoi cung tai Cup C1 hinh anh\" title=\"Buffon nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Cup C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Buffon-nhan-the-do-trong-tran-dau-cuoi-cung-tai-Cup-C1-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Buffon nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a Juve</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11m, si\u00eau sao Cris Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 1 b\u00e0n cho Real Madrid khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Szczesny, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 4-3 chung cu\u1ed9c. K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, trong khi Juve g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Gianlugi Buffon t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Buffon nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin &ldquo;an \u1ee7i&rdquo; ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n 40 tu\u1ed5i. Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 50 tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi sau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 117 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus<br>\r\n</strong><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088661/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Real Madrid vs Juventus<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-kich-ban-tai-bernabeu-nam-ngoai-suc-tuong-tuong-cua-toi-184-184065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/zidane-kich-ban-tai-bernabeu-nam-ngoai-suc-tuong-tuong-cua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-kich-ban-tai-bernabeu-nam-ngoai-suc-tuong-tuong-cua-toi-184-184065.html\">Zidane: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span><br>\r\nZinedine Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real 1-3 Juventus: H\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</span><br>\r\nSu\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa, m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane \u0111\u00e3 an to\u00e0n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid vs...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thong-ke-khong-the-tin-duoc-ve-ronaldo-sau-tran-dau-voi-juventus-184-184062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/ronaldo-hi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thong-ke-khong-the-tin-duoc-ve-ronaldo-sau-tran-dau-voi-juventus-184-184062.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 Ronaldo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Juventus?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Real v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Cristiano Ronaldo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Juventus \u1edf...</d