:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1eadn qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0 \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Buffon ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver d\u1eef d\u1ed9i.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n, Juve c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, khi c\u0169ng n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid 3 b\u00e0n. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, Benatia b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Buffon v\u00ec qu\u00e1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh, v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, gi\u00fap Real gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-3 (sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn). Qu\u00e1 cay c\u00fa v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, Buffon ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t &ldquo;g\u1eaft&rdquo;:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng 1/10 th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng ta nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1edd. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i 11m trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i (c\u1ee7a Juan Cuadrado), b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y?&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\" title=\"Buffon ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/oliver.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Buffon ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t CLB nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00e0o th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn <strong>\u00f4ng ta kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i tim</strong> v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 con v\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng Sprite v\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;<strong>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver</strong>. Real Madrid x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf trong CLB n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00e0 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Lineker \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft (v\u1ec1 nghi v\u1ea5n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n), nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m&rdquo; &ndash; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gianluigi Buffon ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Champions League. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Buffon g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus<br>\r\n</strong><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088661/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Real 1-3 Juve<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-va-ky-niem-buon-trong-tran-cuoi-cung-tai-champions-league-184-184069.html\">Buffon v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-juventus-xung-dang-nhan-duoc-nhung-loi-khen-ngoi-184-184066.html\">Buffon: Juventus x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-kich-ban-tai-bernabeu-nam-ngoai-suc-tuong-tuong-cua-toi-184-184065.html\">Zidane: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real 1-3 Juventus: H\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thong-ke-khong-the-tin-duoc-ve-ronaldo-sau-tran-dau-voi-juventus-184-184062.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 Ronaldo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-tran-real-madrid-13-juve-184-184061.html\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 1-3 Juve</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body><