\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh Tottenham vs Man City vong 34 Ngoai hang Anh hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs Man City v\u00f2ng 34 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Nhan-dinh-Tottenham-vs-Man-City-vong-34-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs Man City t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Spurs \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn. H\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/man-city-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City</strong></span> \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Man xanh c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i NHM, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1eadn Tottenham vs Man City s\u1ebd t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng HLV Pochettino c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. Kyle Walker-Peters d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Man City, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Harry Winks c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane du suc ra san trong tran dau Stoke vs Tottenham\" title=\"Harry Kane \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Stoke vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/tottenham-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-harry-kane.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League v\u1edbi Salah c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1n treo gi\u00f2</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/tottenham-hotspur-5.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tottenham </strong></span>kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2 - </strong>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>1 - </strong>Man City ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 trong 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Tottenham, 4 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 thua 3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>14 -</strong> Tottenham kh\u00f4ng thua trong 14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 11 th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 h\u00f2a.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh toi uu cua Tottenham truoc Man City\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-tottenham-truoc-man-city.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":""