u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tai-sao-mourinho-khong-con-trong-dung-martial-172-184019.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rashford v\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho</span>. Su\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n 1 th\u00e1ng. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean mi\u00ean c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho Martial kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Rashford c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ea1n d\u1ea7n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huyen thoai Arsenal khuyen Martial va Rashford nen roi MU hinh anh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal khuy\u00ean Martial v\u00e0 Rashford n\u00ean r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/4/huyen-thoai-arsenal-khuyen-bo-doi-sao-tre-som-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Wright khuy\u00ean Martial v\u00e0 Rashford n\u00ean r\u1eddi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ian Wright, c\u1ea3 Rashford v\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man United d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMartial v\u00e0 Rashford n\u00ean suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy x\u00e9t t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Man United ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Martial v\u00e0 Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man United \u1edf g\u1ea7n Man City h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa Martial v\u00e0 Mourinho b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nhi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111i th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 Martial\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tai-sao-mourinho-khong-con-trong-dung-martial-172-184019.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/2/tai-sao-mourinho-khong-con-trong-dung-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tai-sao-mourinho-khong-con-trong-dung-martial-172-184019.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng Martial?</span><br>\r\n<span>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng Martial v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCraig Bellamy c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Ian Wright v\u1ec1 Martial v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u01b0a ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch Martial nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 b\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1eaft l\u00e9o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a Mourinho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Rashford, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. N\u1ebfu Man United chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam v\u00e0i t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Rashford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m. D\u00f9 g\u00ec, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-1104-mu-chi-so-tien-khung-mua-hang-thai-chelsea-184-184049.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 11/04: M.U chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-2-muc-tieu-thay-anthony-martial-172-184046.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay Anthony Martial?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-southampton-172-184042.html\">M.U chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Southampton</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-premier-league-172-184020.html\">M.U nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng hot Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-dau-hieu-lon-cho-thay-trung-ve-samuel-umtiti-den-mu-180-183956.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y Umtiti s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-marcus-rashford-khong-nen-roi-mu-172-183946.html\">V\u00ec sao Marcus Rashford kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean r\u1eddi MU?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1059","checkdouble":"184058"},{"date":"00:48 12/04","title":"\"\u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Chelsea n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Diego Costa\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/6/dang-le-chelsea-nen-giu-lai-diego-costa.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial