size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean H\u0110QT VPF kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea7u T\u00fa r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VPF, ph\u00eda HAGL v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 quanh chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 cho HAGL ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea7u T\u00fa kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c \u1edf VPF.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp s\u00e1ng qua 10/4 c\u1ee7a VPF, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a VPF \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed TGQ VPF. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB futsal Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd r\u00fat lui tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o th\u00e2u t\u00f3m quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bau Duc chua co them phan ung sau khi doi thu Tran Anh Tu o lai hinh anh\" title=\"B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00eam ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng sau khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa \u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/17/Bau-Duc-chua-co-them-phan-ung-sau-khi-doi-thu-Tran-Anh-Tu-o-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00eam ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng sau khi '\u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7' Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa \u1edf l\u1ea1i VPF</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea7u T\u00fa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef gh\u1ebf \u1edf VPF c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd d\u1eabn t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u2018cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tranh\u2019 v\u1edbi phe ch\u1ee7 chi\u1ebfn l\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, b\u1ea7u Th\u1eafng. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng b\u1ea7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u00fap m\u1edf vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd cho CLB HAGL r\u1eddi V-League n\u1ebfu b\u1ea7u T\u00fa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef gh\u1ebf VPF v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a VFF. V\u00e0 sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ph\u00eda HAGL v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m c\u0103ng \u1edf v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh th\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0o t\u1eeb b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh r\u00fat HAGL kh\u1ecfi V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ea7u T\u00fa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0m TG\u0110 VPF, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1edbi t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ecb doanh nh\u00e2n qu\u00ea B\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c cho hay m\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n \u0111i c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#081f2c;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-tu-mong-duoc-bau-duc-va-bau-thang-ton-trong-168-184016.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/bau-tu-mong-duoc-bau-duc-va-bau-thang-ton-trong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-tu-mong-duoc-bau-duc-va-bau-thang-ton-trong-168-184016.html\">B\u1ea7u T\u00fa mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 b\u1ea7u Th\u1eafng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VPF b\u1ea7u T\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, b\u1ea7u Th\u1eafng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1057","checkdouble":"184030"},{"date":"16:13 11/04","title":"VFF ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/vff-ra-an-phat-chinh-thuc-cho-hau-ve-tang-tien.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}